text:
Gabby: My whole life,
my mom and sister

have been doing
these great things,

and I've always just been
the family screw-up.

- Are you watching me?
- Of course, I am.

This is my chance
to do something great, too.
I require a babysitter to keep

- our alien identities secret.
- Yeah, I'm in.

And I can't tell my best friend
who loves aliens.

Have you observed anything
out of the ordinary?

This is so
out of the ordinary!

- Nope. Nada.
- Keeping it all a secret

from the people I love?
Wish me luck.
That went better than I-- aah!
